name: Marcus Machado - Pass Me By (Feat. T. Fox)

metadata.description:
Pass Me By Feat.TFox

The song “Pass Me By” is about a relationship of wanting to be
In someone’s world so bad that you was willing to do anything 
just to be on their side. But then you realize that you are worth more 
and deserved better. In the end it had to be all or nothing.

I'm a Guitarist heavily influenced by Jimi Hendrix, Prince & Sly Stone. I wanna merge the worlds of R&B & Rock together which I like to call it Psychedelic Soul. 


Enjoy the vibes 
Marcusy
